- Setting Up API's and Mock Data using JSON Server:

    - We can use any framework, language, any server setup for APIs
    - We can use Cloud hosted APIs and Mock Endpoints

    - JSON Server
        - npm i --save json-server
        - default port for json server is 3000
        - best practice is to keep all the mock data in the assests folder
        - https://github.com/typicode/json-server  -> we can copy dummy json from this link
        - create a new file with db.json to store the data
        - json-server --watch .\db.json -> to run the json-server



- Install Bootstrap

    - Bootstrap 4 
        - npm i --save bootstrap jquery popper

    - Bootstrap 5
        - npm i --save bootstrap popper (Bootstrap 5 does not require jquery)